  m_text: 'Your extraction value failed to meet minimum corporate thresholds. You
    have been classified as a redundant asset. Security is en route to repossess
    your uniform.


    We would thank you for your time, but alas, that would be
    dishotest. We will make sure to mark your name down in our "Don''t Hire Again"
    list. Good riddance.'
